summary: This is intended for the creation of an NPC follower.
descriptionHtml:
A friend of mine wants to help me make my character into a Follower so I\'m uploading this for him.
I suppose if any one else wants to use this I have no problem with that. but do let me know just so I can check out the mod you created. or if you just want to use it for you\'re self than go for it.

really it\'s just a save game and an SPF  and the save game olready has some quest complreted.
